<p />
<h2 class="twikinetRoundedAttachments"><span class="twikinetHeader"><a name="Workflows"></a> Workflows </span></h2>
<p />
Each workflow is described along with its capability requirements.
<p />
<h3><a name="1_Send_data_to_a_Job"></a> 1 Send data to a Job </h3>
<p /> <ol>
<li> A CE/SE combination is chosen
</li></ol> 
<p />
<h4><a name="1_Capability_Requirements"></a> 1 Capability Requirements </h4>
<p /> <ol>
<li> Knowledge or discovery of authorized CE/SE combo.
</li></ol> 
<p />
<h4><a name="1_Workflow_Scenario"></a> 1 Workflow Scenario </h4>
<p />
<h3><a name="2_Send_a_job_to_Data"></a> 2 Send a job to Data </h3>
<p /> <ol>
<li> CEs and the SE are not related, except for the merge job.
</li></ol> 
<p />
<h4><a name="2_Capability_Requirements"></a> 2 Capability Requirements </h4>
<p /> <ol>
<li> Knowledge or discovery of authorized CEs and CE/SE combo.
</li></ol> 
<p />
<h4><a name="1_Workflow_Scenario_AN1"></a> 1 Workflow Scenario </h4>
<p />
<h3><a name="3_Run_a_job_using_locally_stored"></a> 3 Run a job using locally-stored product of a previous job </h3>
<p />
<h3><a name="4_Run_a_job_using_locally_stored"></a> 4 Run a job using locally-stored products of several previous jobs </h3>
<p />
<h3><a name="5_Run_a_job_using_remotely_store"></a> 5 Run a job using remotely-stored products of several previous jobs </h3>
<p />
<h3><a name="6_Stage_data_to_a_site_then_run"></a> 6 Stage data to a site, then run jobs on it </h3>
<p />
